             were indicted; the first for <rs id="t17810425-37-off177" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17810425-37-off177" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17810425-37-off177" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17810425-37-cd178" type="crimeDate">11th of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17810425-37-off177 t17810425-37-cd178"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17810425-37-off179 t17810425-37-cd178"></join>, a silver watch, value 3 l. a pair of pinchbeck shoe-buckles, value 1 s. three guineas and eight shillings, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17810425-37-victim392" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Downs
                        <interp inst="t17810425-37-victim392" type="surname" value="Downs"></interp>
